msgid "The Awakening"
msgstr "苏醒"

msgid "Interlude III: The Awakening"
msgstr "幕间故事III：苏醒"

msgid ""
"A violent tremor knocks you prone. As you clamber to your feet, Ruby suppresses a gasp. A heavy shadow appears, veiled in the sepulchral darkness within the gates. A steady pulse—like a heartbeat—ripples through the city's nightmarish skyline. The ancient monstrosity drags himself on his belly through the gate."
"The gargantuan beast sways unsteadily. He is easily the size of a small mountain, with sickly green skin, an octopoid head and face, and a set of limp, tattered wings. Your vision doubles as you look at him, as if the creature were both here and elsewhere, both metaphysical and physical. The stench of his ancient rotten flesh is almost enough to make you retch."
"The thing's red eyes glow as he gazes down on you. A steady, insistent weight presses down on your shoulders, forcing you to kneel. You hear yourself speaking in a voice not quite your own: \"[tdc_rune_u][tdc_rune_c][tdc_rune_b][tdc_rune_n][tdc_rune_p][tdc_rune_b][tdc_rune_n] [tdc_rune_a][tdc_rune_b][tdc_rune_c][tdc_rune_d][tdc_rune_e][tdc_rune_f]!\""
msgstr ""
"剧烈的震颤将你晃倒。你刚站起来，露比就倒抽一口凉气。门内阴森的黑暗中浮现出一个沉重的阴影。古城夜魇般的天际线一阵稳当的搏动—有如心跳。这只远古怪物拖着肚子穿过门扉。"
"巨兽摇摇晃晃，他快有一座小山那么大，长着恶心的绿皮，章鱼的头面，一对柔软破碎的翅膀。你望向他，居然有了重影，仿佛他既在此又在彼，既在脑海又在现实。他远古腐肉的臭气几乎让你作呕。"
"他怒视着你，红眼发出光来。你肩上不断积累起重压，迫使你跪下。你听到自己用不属于你的声音说道：“[tdc_rune_u][tdc_rune_c][tdc_rune_b][tdc_rune_n][tdc_rune_p][tdc_rune_b][tdc_rune_n] [tdc_rune_a][tdc_rune_b][tdc_rune_c][tdc_rune_d][tdc_rune_e][tdc_rune_f]！”"

msgid "Check Campaign Log. If there is at least 1 artifact marked in \"Artifacts Obtained\""
msgstr "检查剧本日志。如果在“取得的神器”下有至少1个神器打了勾,"

msgid ""
"\"Look away!\" shouts Ruby. You turn to see your companions also kneeling before the awful dead dreaming god. A warmth spreads through your body as he delves deep into your mind, your memories. The warm feeling gives way to something cold, hateful. Looking up, you see him staring back at you, his fifth eye open."
"You feel his rage. You have taken part of his domain. You must perish."
msgstr ""
"“快别看了！”露比叫道。你转过去看自己的同伴，但他们已经在可怕的已逝入梦的神灵面前跪下。他深入了你的思维、你的记忆，你竟感到一阵温暖遍布全身，温暖很快就变成了冰冷和憎恨。你抬头看去，发现他也凝视着你，张开了第五只眼。"
"你感受到了他的愤怒：你侵犯了他的领域。你必须得死。"

msgid "Remove all [cultist], [tablet], and [elder_thing] tokens form the chaos bag. Then add 2 [cultist], 2 [tablet] and 2 [elder_thing] tokens for the remainder of the campaign."
msgstr "从混乱袋中移除所有[cultist]，[tablet]和[elder_thing]标记。然后，在本剧本剩余时间内，在混乱袋中加入2个[cultist]标记、2个[tablet]标记和2个[elder_thing]标记。"

msgid ""
"\"Look away!\" shouts Ruby. You turn to see your companions also kneeling before the awful dead dreaming god. A warmth spreads through your body as he delves deep into your mind, your memories. Great Cthulhu turns his gaze away from you, northward. In your mind, you see the image of the small green idol on Randall's desk in Arkham. The warm feeling gives way to something cold, hateful. Looking up, you see Great Cthulhu staring back at you, his fifth dreaming eye open."
"You feel his rage at the one who stole part of his domain. They must perish."
msgstr ""
"“快别看了！”露比叫道。你转过去看自己的同伴，但他们已经在可怕的已逝入梦的神灵面前跪下。他深入了你的思维、你的记忆，你竟感到一阵温暖遍布全身，伟大之克苏鲁不再看你，而是怒视北方。你的脑海中出现了阿卡姆市里兰道尔桌上小小的绿色偶像。温暖很快就变成了冰冷和憎恨。你抬头看去，发现他也凝视着你，张开了第五只入梦之眼。"
"你感受到了他的愤怒：有人盗窃了他的领域。这人必须得死。"

msgid "Remove all [cultist], [tablet], and [elder_thing] tokens form the chaos bag. Then add [cultist], [tablet] and 2 [elder_thing] tokens for the remainder of the campaign."
msgstr "从混乱袋中移除所有[cultist]，[tablet]和[elder_thing]标记。然后，在本剧本剩余时间内，在混乱袋中加入1个[cultist]标记、[tablet]个标记和2个[elder_thing]标记。"

msgid ""
"Struggling against the ancient one's terrible will, you rise and help the others to their feet. Great Cthulhu grasps at you with sinewy tentacles as you flee to the water's edge and paddle furiously toward the <i>Cassandra.</i> Once aboard, the ship threads a narrow strait through a gauntlet of risen spires and deadly shoals to reach the open ocean."
"An ear splitting roar echoes across the water. You turn to see the colossal abomination slip greasily into the black water and out of view. You stare down into the fathomless deep, waiting to see five angry red eyes emerge to capsize the ship. The nightmarish skyline of R'lyeh glimmers with pale green fire as it fades into the distance. A minute passes, then ten, then thirty. There is no movement, no stirring in the depths. The abomination may have lost interest, or perhaps gotten tangled in the shoals. Or, at least, so you hope."
msgstr ""
"你奋力抵抗古神的可怕意志，还帮助其他人也站了起来。伟大之克苏鲁伸出道劲的触手抓向了你，而你逃到水边，拼命划向<i>卡珊德拉号。</i>一等你上船，船就穿过狭窄的海峡，经过危险的高耸尖塔和浅滩，抵达了开阔的洋面。"
"震耳欲聋的吼叫响彻整片水域。你扭头看去，发现庞大的怪物滑回了黑水，消失在视域中。你低头望向无尽的深海，以为那五只愤怒的红眼晴会再度浮现，弄翻船只。拉莱耶梦魇般的天际线闪着惨绿色的火光，渐渐消失在远处。一分钟过去了，十分钟过去了，半小时过去了。没什么东西在动，深海一片平静。这头怪物可能失去了兴趣，或者困在了浅滩之中。至少，你是这么希望的。"
